01:37:23,366 --> 01:37:24,958
Officer on deck!

1272
01:37:41,686 --> 01:37:45,122
- Who are all these kids?
- We got reinforced.

1273
01:37:45,206 --> 01:37:47,322
Most of them are
fresh out of boot.

1274
01:37:47,406 --> 01:37:49,158
