1275
01:37:51,446 --> 01:37:53,596
This is for all you new people.

1276
01:37:53,686 --> 01:37:55,836
I only have one rule:

1277
01:37:55,926 --> 01:37:58,884
Everyone fights.
No one quits.

1278
01:37:58,966 --> 01:38:01,924
If you don't do your job,
I'll kill you myself.

1279
01:38:02,006 --> 01:38:03,234
Do you get me?

1280
01:38:03,326 --> 01:38:05,282
We get you, sir!

1281
01:38:05,366 --> 01:38:09,837
- Welcome to the Roughnecks.
- Rico's Roughnecks!

1282
01:38:12,366 --> 01:38:14,834
Today we're gonna pay
a visit to Bug City.

1283
01:38:14,926 --> 01:38:18,077
We're lookin' for a bug
no one's ever seen before.

1284
01:38:18,166 --> 01:38:19,918
Some kind of smart bug.

1285
01:38:25,606 --> 01:38:27,483
And it probably knows
we're comin'.

1286
01:38:27,566 --> 01:38:31,320
- Saddle up!
- Saddle up now!

1287
01:38:31,406 --> 01:38:33,203
Come on!
Run, run, run, run, run!

1288
01:38:44,206 --> 01:38:46,083
Evasive action.

1289
01:39:08,486 --> 01:39:10,204
Get us clear for warp,
Number Two.

1290
01:39:10,286 --> 01:39:12,595
Clear in five, four...

1291
01:39:12,686 --> 01:39:14,563
- Initiating star drive...
- three-
