- Abandon ship! Come on!

1294
01:39:44,806 --> 01:39:46,797
Carmen! Oh!

1295
01:39:46,886 --> 01:39:49,525
- Zander!
- Here!

1296
01:39:49,606 --> 01:39:52,598
- We've got to get to the rescue deck!
- Come on!

1297
01:40:08,486 --> 01:40:09,760
Captain!

1298
01:40:12,646 --> 01:40:15,365
Abandon ship.
That's an-

1299
01:40:16,806 --> 01:40:19,274
She's dead, Carmen.
She's dead!

