01:40:35,926 --> 01:40:38,645
Go! Here!

1301
01:40:53,446 --> 01:40:54,765
Follow me!

1302
01:41:06,006 --> 01:41:07,121
Ready?

1303
01:41:13,326 --> 01:41:14,645
Hit it!

1304
01:41:31,526 --> 01:41:34,199
Life pod Bravo 6-3,
two aboard.

1305
01:41:41,526 --> 01:41:45,997
Scanning for a landing zone!
Checking terrain. Here!

1306
01:41:46,086 --> 01:41:48,077
- Can you handle that?
- Piece of cake.

1307
01:41:51,726 --> 01:41:54,160
- We've lost the Rodger Young!
- What is your position?

1308
01:41:54,246 --> 01:41:57,682
Flight Command, we have confirmation.
The Rodger Young is down.

1309
01:41:57,766 --> 01:41:59,438
- Oh. Johnny!
- This is Flight Command.

1310
01:41:59,526 --> 01:42:01,517
Please repeat.
Please repeat.

1311
01:42:01,606 --> 01:42:05,042
- Johnny!
- We now have confirmation.
Rodger Young is down.

1312
01:42:05,126 --> 01:42:07,003
- I repeat, Rodger Young is down.
- Rodger Young just burned up.

1313
01:42:07,086 --> 01:42:10,317
- It's on the rescue net.
- Life pod Bravo 6-3, two aboard.

1314
01:42:10,406 --> 01:42:13,204
- Is anyone receiving?
- Any survivors?
- Is anyone receiving?

1315
01:42:13,286 --> 01:42:15,800
- Well, they're getting tarred
up there pretty bad.
- Life pod...

1316
01:42:15,886 --> 01:42:17,205
Bravo 6-3, two aboard.

1317
01:42:17,286 --> 01:42:18,799
Is anyone receiving?

1318
01:42:18,886 --> 01:42:20,205
- Is anyone receiving?
- Affirmative.

1319
01:42:20,286 --> 01:42:21,719
This is Roughneck 2-0.

1320
01:42:21,806 --> 01:42:23,285
You're breaking up.
Say again.

1321
01:42:23,366 --> 01:42:25,641
- Carmen?
- Say again. I'm losing you.

1322
01:42:25,726 --> 01:42:27,000
Carmen!

1323
01:42:30,766 --> 01:42:32,085
Prepare for landing.

1324
01:42:32,166 --> 01:42:33,918
Retros in three...

1325
01:42:34,006 --> 01:42:36,395
two, one, fire!

1326
01:42:51,806 --> 01:42:53,524
Carmen. Carmen.

1327
01:42:53,606 --> 01:42:55,676
- Hey, are you okay?
- Uh-huh.

1328
01:42:55,766 --> 01:42:57,119
Get out.
Get out.

1329
01:43:06,366 --> 01:43:10,325
This is Roughneck 2-0. Are you
receiving? Over. This is Roughneck 2-0.

1330
01:43:10,406 --> 01:43:13,716
- Carmen, are you receiving?
- Johnny, is that you?
- Yeah!

1331
01:43:13,806 --> 01:43:16,400
- It's me! Wh-What's your
position and situation?
- Yeah.

1332
01:43:16,486 --> 01:43:18,044
We're in Bug City,
20 metres underground.

1333
01:43:18,126 --> 01:43:21,243
Position:
south 42, east 118.

1334
01:43:21,326 --> 01:43:23,282
Situation is-

1335
01:43:23,366 --> 01:43:25,084
I repeat.
South 42, east 118.

1336
01:43:25,166 --> 01:43:27,475
What's your situation?
Over.

1337
01:43:27,566 --> 01:43:28,885
Carmen.

1338
01:43:31,046 --> 01:43:32,877
Situation is
extremely hostile.

1339
01:43:37,606 --> 01:43:39,483
I need a squad
to pull 'em out!

1340
01:43:39,566 --> 01:43:41,682
- Direction?
- Three clicks, south by southwest.

1341
01:43:47,886 --> 01:43:49,524
Look out!

1342
01:44:07,686 --> 01:44:10,075
- What do you wanna do?
- You heard the lieutenant.

1343
01:44:10,166 --> 01:44:14,318
Rescue party!
Third squad, come with me!

1344
01:44:14,406 --> 01:44:16,715
Cancel that!

1345
01:44:16,806 --> 01:44:19,445
You know as well as I do,
she's already dead.

1346
01:44:22,726 --> 01:44:24,000
Sorry, buddy.

1347
01:44:25,926 --> 01:44:29,362
Roughnecks, let's move.

1348
01:44:29,446 --> 01:44:31,437
All right.

1349
01:44:45,606 --> 01:44:47,437
Why didn't they kill us?

1350
01:44:47,526 --> 01:44:49,596
They want us alive.

1351
01:45:41,366 --> 01:45:43,596
We should go this way.

1352
01:45:44,886 --> 01:45:47,195
A Company's that way.

1353
01:45:47,286 --> 01:45:51,359
Yeah, but Carmen's
down there.

1354
01:45:51,446 --> 01:45:54,643
Hey, I hate to be rude, buddy,
but word has it she's dead.

1355
01:45:56,086 --> 01:45:57,280
She's still alive.

1356
01:45:57,366 --> 01:45:59,516
How do you know?

1357
01:45:59,606 --> 01:46:02,200
- I don't know how I know, but I know.
- Listen.

1358
01:46:02,286 --> 01:46:04,595
You got command,
but going off mission--

1359
01:46:04,686 --> 01:46:06,961
- That's a serious offence.
- Yeah.

1360
01:46:07,046 --> 01:46:08,923
I think they
hang you for that.

1361
01:46:11,046 --> 01:46:14,721
Roughneck 2-0,
proceed on mission.

1362
01:46:14,806 --> 01:46:17,320
I need two volunteers.

1363
01:47:25,248 --> 01:47:26,681
One day...

1364
01:47:26,768 --> 01:47:29,077
someone like me...

1365
01:47:29,168 --> 01:47:30,840
is gonna kill you...

1366
01:47:30,928 --> 01:47:32,964
and your whole fucking race.

1367
01:48:29,608 --> 01:48:30,723
You know what this is?

1368
01:48:33,608 --> 01:48:34,882
Sure you do.

1369
01:48:36,408 --> 01:48:38,876
You're some kind
of big, fat, smart bug...

1370
01:48:38,968 --> 01:48:40,242
aren't you?

1371
01:48:42,368 --> 01:48:44,279
Come on.

1372
01:48:55,208 --> 01:48:56,926
This is Roughneck 2-0.

1373
01:48:57,008 --> 01:49:00,478
Brain Bug sighted moving
west of grid five.

1374
01:49:02,648 --> 01:49:04,001
Run!

1375
01:49:32,888 --> 01:49:35,243
Go! Go!

1376
01:49:35,328 --> 01:49:38,638
- Give me the nuke!
- You trying to be a hero, Watkins?

1377
01:49:40,728 --> 01:49:43,959
I'm trying to kill
some bugs, sir!

1378
01:49:44,048 --> 01:49:47,085
Get outta here!
Get outta here!

1379
01:49:48,568 --> 01:49:49,842
Move!

1380
01:49:54,328 --> 01:49:57,445
Come on! You like that?
You like that? Come on!

1381
01:49:57,528 --> 01:49:58,802
You want a little more?

1382
01:50:02,088 --> 01:50:05,046
You like that? You like that?
You like that? You like that?
You want a little more?

1383
01:50:11,008 --> 01:50:12,157
Come on! Come on!

1384
01:50:17,288 --> 01:50:18,562
Come on, come on, come on!

1385
01:50:42,088 --> 01:50:43,237
Come on, Carmen.

1386
01:50:55,048 --> 01:50:57,482
- We did it!
- We won!

1387
01:51:02,568 --> 01:51:04,718
- What's going on?
- They got it!

1388
01:51:04,808 --> 01:51:05,923
Come on!

1389
01:51:18,848 --> 01:51:22,761
Pull! Pull! Pull!

1390
01:51:34,208 --> 01:51:36,119
Quiet!

1391
01:51:47,208 --> 01:51:49,358
What's it thinking, Colonel?

1392
01:52:06,688 --> 01:52:07,916
It's afraid.

1393
01:52:09,328 --> 01:52:10,556
It's afraid!

1394
01:52:14,488 --> 01:52:17,719
- Come on.
- Yeah!

1395
01:52:17,808 --> 01:52:20,117
Carl! Carl! Hey!

1396
01:52:20,208 --> 01:52:23,006
Well, look who's here.
You made it. Good.

1397
01:52:23,088 --> 01:52:26,239
It was you, wasn't it?
You told me how to find Carmen.

1398
01:52:26,328 --> 01:52:27,761
Well, that's classified.

1399
01:52:29,808 --> 01:52:32,447
You know, whenever
the three of us are together...

1400
01:52:32,528 --> 01:52:35,326
I feel like things
might just work out.

1401
01:52:35,408 --> 01:52:37,239
I hope you're right,
Carmen.

1402
01:52:37,328 --> 01:52:40,126
We've got one of their Brains now.
Pretty soon we'll know how they think.

1403
01:52:40,208 --> 01:52:42,676
And then we'll know
how to beat them.

1404
01:52:42,768 --> 01:52:44,759
One day it will all be over...

1405
01:52:44,848 --> 01:52:47,646
and everyone will forget
that this was the moment.

1406
01:52:47,728 --> 01:52:50,526
This is when it turned.

1407
01:52:50,608 --> 01:52:54,521
And it wasn't the mighty Fleet,
it wasn't some fancy new weapon.

1408
01:52:58,288 --> 01:53:01,246
It was a drill instructor named Zim
who captured a Brain.

1409
01:53:01,328 --> 01:53:02,841
Come on!
Who am I?

1410
01:53:02,928 --> 01:53:04,964
- Yeah!
- Zim?

1411
01:53:06,328 --> 01:53:08,558
He got him! Yeah!

1412
01:53:08,648 --> 01:53:10,798
Zim. Zim got the bug.

1413
01:53:10,888 --> 01:53:12,401
Zim got the bug, man!

1414
01:53:12,488 --> 01:53:15,639
- Good job, Sergeant.
- Thank you, sir.

1415
01:53:15,728 --> 01:53:20,358
- That would be private, sir.
- Carry on, Private.

1416
01:53:20,448 --> 01:53:22,962
- Yes, sir!
- Yeah!

1417
01:53:27,208 --> 01:53:30,166
What mysteries
will the Brain Bug reveal?

1418
01:53:30,248 --> 01:53:34,958
Federal scientists are working
around the clock to probe its secrets.

1419
01:53:35,048 --> 01:53:38,404
Once we understand the bug,
we will defeat it.

1420
01:53:44,328 --> 01:53:45,761
We have the ships.

