prepare for drop.

1427
01:53:59,688 --> 01:54:02,327
Soldiers like Private Ace Levy
and Lieutenant John Rico.

1428
01:54:02,408 --> 01:54:05,764
Come on, you apes!
You wanna live forever?

1429
01:54:05,848 --> 01:54:07,247
We need you all.

1430
01:54:07,328 --> 01:54:10,638
Service guarantees citizenship.
